NUMBER 740
NAME Teeth of Shartan, Lakeside Road
ITEM 9 693
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The roots of the few trees standing near the old road have pushed up a great section of it here, demonstrating the dauntless efforts of nature to reclaim her domain. In older days, these trees may have been trimmed or cut down, but now it is the trees which are pruning the road. Strange rustling noises come from under the needles and patches of melting snow as a tiny squirrel roots around for a bit of food.
*DESCRIPTION_END
MOUNTAIN
DAY_LIGHT
MONSTER_GROUP 26
EXIT NE 739
EXIT S 741
