NUMBER 741
NAME Teeth of Shartan, Lakeside Road
ITEM 9 693
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Some distance out in the lake from the road lies a square stone structure, its sides open to admit a roaring flow of water from the lake. Only a few inches of the structure are visible above the surface of the lake. Chunks of ice broken from the surface of the lake collide and briefly jam the openings, and then disappear into the structure.
*DESCRIPTION_END
MOUNTAIN
DAY_LIGHT
MONSTER_GROUP 26
EXIT ABOVE 4
EXIT N 740
EXIT SW  733
