NAME Teeth of Shartan, Lover's Leap
ITEM 9 693
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
A rocky promentory juts out from the cliff face and hangs high over the
clear blue waters of the lake far below. The entire lake, the stands of
uquart, and the winding valley seem tiny compared to this lofty vantage
point. An ancient uquart tree stands near the precipice, its gnarled roots
clinging tenuously to the rocks of the ledge. A large sign warns of the
danger of the long drop.
*DESCRIPTION_END
