	CLEARVERB
	IFVAR abjumpfl = 1
		ECHO GROUP With great determination, you leap over the edge of the cliff, and fall towards the deep blue waters of the lake below. You feel a tremendous sense of inner calm as you accelerate towards the water. Just before you hit the surface, you feel detatched and free from your body.
		ECHO GROUP Of course, the impact with the water is entirely lethal.
		ECHO OTHGROUP %P just leaped over the edge to certain death!
		ECHO GROUP Your lifeless body washes up on the shore of the lake.
		MOVEGROUP 40
		KILL ALL
		MOVEGROUP 739
		AFFECT 739
    ECHO GROUP Your body washes up on shore.
		ECHO OTHGROUP %P washes up on the shore liflessly.
		AFFECT 745
		EQUAL abjumpfl 0
	ELSE
		ECHO GROUP You stand near the edge of the cliff and ponder the drop, but you can't quite manage the courage to leap over the edge.
		ECHO OTHGROUP %P looks mournfully over the edge of the cliff.
		EQUAL abjumpfl 1
	ENDIF
ENDIF
