NUMBER 944
NAME Fang of Shartan, basin
ITEM 9 693
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Jagged rocks ring this deep basin on all sides, forming a bowl atop the mountain with sides well above your head. A platform of solid stone with raised edges is set in the ground here. A well-traveled path leads up through the rocks to the edge of the mountain where a few palely blooming, scraggly weeds find purchase.
*DESCRIPTION_END
LIMITED_MOVEMENT
DAY_LIGHT
MOUNTAIN
