MONSTER_GROUP 12
PLAIN
DAY_LIGHT
ITEM 9 693
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The road ringing Fayd meets at the back wall of the town and runs off to the west. The iron walls are covered with graffiti, some of it obscenity written by youngsters, but there are also messages to and from adventurers, detailing meeting spots and times. Some of the more obscure messages are thought to be coded Thieves Guild instructions. The noise and commotion of the front gate is absent here, the quiet only broken by the occasional muffled cry of a street vendor coming over the wall.
*DESCRIPTION_END
